  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述Groupware IssueTracker的工作流程。系统启动后应该进入Creating状态，然后分叉成Writer和Reader两个独立的工作流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Creating是入口状态。Writer和Reader是两个并行状态还是嵌套状态？我倾向于做成嵌套状态，这样结构更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，嵌套状态。Writer内部关联Groupware ChatRoom，从ChatRoom进入Writing，然后正常结束时要经过Disconnecting和ClosingReader，最后回到Creating。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Writer",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom",
        "Writing",
        "Disconnecting",
        "ClosingReader",
        "Creating"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Writer分支我画好了。那Reader这边呢？也是类似的流程吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Writer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Reader这边略有不同。它从Groupware IssueTracker开始Reading，但可能会遇到Error异常，然后走ClosingWriter回到Creating。注意这里是ClosingWriter不是ClosingReader。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reader",
        "Groupware_IssueTracker",
        "Reading",
        "Error",
        "ClosingWriter",
        "Creating"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我注意到一个问题。Writer分支最后是ClosingReader，Reader分支最后是ClosingWriter，这两个命名是不是反了？Writer结束应该关闭Writer，Reader结束应该关闭Reader才合理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClosingReader",
        "ClosingWriter",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不，命名是对的。这是交叉清理机制：Writer正常结束时需要清理关联的Reader资源，所以是ClosingReader；Reader异常退出时需要清理Writer资源，所以是ClosingWriter。这是故意设计的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClosingReader",
        "ClosingWriter",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，交叉清理的设计。那我补充最后一条线：Creating还要能回到Groupware IssueTracker形成完整闭环。图完成了，您看一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
